    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the 510(k) hemolysis tolerance decision for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. Physical fault tolerance for sensor failure, actuator wear, and electrical anomalies encountered during extended in vivo deployment is documented elsewhere and considered outside the scope of this credibility assessment.",
